metadata.name: OGRE UNIVERSE #000 - Legacy4 ONE+TWO
metadata.description:
This is our first NFT on the Foundation.

This picture is part of the story in the Thai cartoon LEGACY4 that we created.

For coloring This image has been colored with Copic. which is the method of coloring on paper that we specialize in The colors come out beautifully in a manga style.
.
LEGACY4
Story by ARUNTIWA
ART by MONTRI K.
.
